alking at once. Mrs. Kozlov took Peter by the wrist, led him down a short flight of steps between tubbed laurels and oleanders, and with an air of mystery pointed gardenward: “You will find them there,” she said; “go and join them,” whereupon she returned to her guests. Peter remained standing on the lower step.

